Package uk.ac.leedsbeckett.oop

Class TrackCell

java.lang.Object
uk.ac.leedsbeckett.oop.Cell
uk.ac.leedsbeckett.oop.TrackCell
Direct Known Subclasses:
CornerTrack, CrossingTrack, RailCell, StraightTrack
public abstract class TrackCell extends Cell
Abstract base class for all track cells in the railway system. A track cell represents a piece of railway track at a specific position with connections in one or more directions. Each track cell can be occupied by at most one vehicle at a time.
